KeamilKindhearted, what kind of Crack are you smoking.<br>
<br>
Not every monk in the game has access to the types of equipment you are listing out here.  TStaff is the most common one, and it goes for 25-50k pp depending what server you are on.  All the TStaff does it put the monk ahead of the curve.  By the time a monk has access to Primal/Luclin weapons, other cases have access to almost ~ weapons.  <br>
